<br>
starmetal + forging hammer + chisel = SM piece + hammer + chisel <br>
SM piece + dragon bone dust = dusted SM + remaining bone dust (I failed here, last night)<br>
Dusted SM + hammer + chisel = first fold <br>
first fold + hammer + chisel = 2nd fold <br>
... <br>
fourth fold + hammer + chisel = 5th fold <br>
5th fold + hammer = <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> core completed </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
StarMetal piece + remaining bone dust = Dusted SM (!!) <br>
dustd SM + hammer + chisel = first fold <br>
first fold + hammer + chisel = 2nd fold <br>
... <br>
9th fold + hammer + chisel = 10th fold <br>
10th fold + core + hammer + chisel = combined <br>
combined + hammer = raw blade <br>
raw blade + clay mix = clayed blade <br>
clayed blade + grey ice = <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> completed blade. </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
And then you are done with the smithing! Yes???<br>
<br>
Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>
